      <span class="tg-hero__type">Book Study · Matthew 5–7</span>
      <h1 class="tg-hero__title">The Sermon on the Mount</h1>
      <p class="tg-hero__intro">
        Jesus' inaugural manifesto of the Kingdom of God — the most concentrated body of
        ethical and spiritual teaching in all of Scripture.
      </p>
      <blockquote class="tg-hero__key-verse">
        <p>Blessed are the poor in spirit, for theirs is the kingdom of heaven.</p>
        <cite><a class="ref" data-ref="Matthew 5:3">Matthew 5:3</a></cite>
      </blockquote>
    </div>
  </header><main>
    <div class="container">

      <nav class="tg-toc" aria-label="Study contents">
        <h2 class="tg-toc__title">Contents</h2>
        <ol class="tg-toc__list">
          <li><a href="#context">Setting and Background</a></li>
          <li><a href="#beatitudes">The Beatitudes (5:3–12)</a></li>
